data.description: This 2-bedroom 1.5 bath home conveniently located, offers easy access to nearby parks and shopping centers. Easy access to transportation routes, commuting is a breeze, allowing you to explore all the attractions and amenities that Canal Winchester has to offer.  The 2 spaces bedrooms provides plenty of space for a growing family or for hosting guests. The bedrooms are filled with natural light and provide a peaceful retreat to unwind after a long day.  Schedule your showing today. You don't want to miss this one.
